---
layout: default
---
<article class="mx-auto prose md:prose-lg lg:prose-xl xl:prose-2xl">
  <h1>Latest Blog Posts</h1>
  {% if collections.blog %}
  <ul>
    {% for post in collections.blog | reverse %}
      {% if loop.index0 < 5 %}
      <li>
        <a href="{{ post.url }}"> {{ post.data.title }} </a>
      </li>
      {% endif %}
    {% endfor %}
  </ul>
  {% endif %}
  <p>Go to my <a href='/blog'>Blog</a> to see all of my posts.</p>

</article>